(142, 'product_main_description', '<p>Get an overview of the total number of projects, tasks, bugs, and members. A visual representation of the task overview and project status can help you estimate the progress on each task. Lastly, you can check the top due task.</p>', 'Taskly', '2024-06-24 19:15:50', '2024-06-24 19:15:50'),
