(3, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br>Mr. salutation Mr. Hardy,</p>\n<p>Thank you very much for your inquiry and the nice on-site inspection appointment.</p>\n<p>As discussed, our construction managers have now calculated your request in detail. Attached you will find our offer for your construction project in Tempelhofer Ufer, 17, 10963 Berlin .</p>\n<p>We took our time planning and incorporated all the details discussed into our offer as much as possible. Our team has already carried out many renovations and based on our experience we can guarantee you a very clean implementation.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Timeline:&nbsp;</strong>approx. 2-3 months, starting from&nbsp;09/12/2024</li>\n<li><strong>Payment plan:</strong>&nbsp; gradually according to the acceptance protocol</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In the appendix you will find our standard construction contract according to VOB, which regulates all important points about your construction project.</p>\n<p>If you would like to commission our team to carry out the implementation, please let us know at short notice so that we can plan for this in terms of capacity. This is followed by a final construction meeting on site.</p>\n<p>If you have an alternative offer, we would like to ask you to give us the opportunity to examine it. We would then be happy to discuss with you and our construction managers what services or positions we can adapt to our offering if necessary.</p>\n<p>If you have any questions, we are of course welcome to call you or meet again on site.</p>\n<p>We would be happy about a collaboration. Thank you in advance for your timely feedback.</p>', 'Estimation 17 - TEST 77 - Tempelhofer Ufer, 17 - Berlin - #120 - Neuwest GmbH.pdf', 2, NULL, 3, '2024-08-22 09:19:43', '2024-08-22 09:19:43');
